Rating, 5 stars,  · June 2023,  · Stayed with kids
rating_comment:
The apartment was okay. The apartment contains some problems.
1. The AC is not working correctly, it takes a long time to be cold
2. Water comes from the top of the outer sink, and the floor gets wet frequently.
3. The flush of the main attached bathroom is not working properly
4. In the morning, a lot of dogs bark, which is really disgusting
5. There is no gas pressure in the kitchen
I think if someone wants to take this apartment, please first contact the owner and make sure whether those problem solved.

rating_comment: The house direction was very precise and easy to find. The neighborhood is peaceful and welcoming. The house manager is always ready to help and very responsible.
